Package edu.cmu.cs214.hw5.framework.core

Class AugmentedDataSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cmu.cs214.hw5.framework.core.AugmentedDataSet
  • public final class AugmentedDataSet
extends java.lang.Object
    A wrapper containing two RawDataSet objects. The first represents historical data obtained from a data source, while the second represents predicted data generated by a forecast model. An AugmentedDataSet is created by a ModelPlugin and passed to a DisplayPlugin to be visualized. The time-distance between data points in the prediction is stored as a ModelPlugin.PredictionIncrement.
